item.title: CVE-2020-4310|2024-09-17T01:10:57.169Z -- ibm -- websphere%20mq
item.description: IBM MQ and MQ Appliance 7.1, 7.5, 8.0, 9.0 LTS, 9.1 LTS, and 9.1 C are vulnerable to a denial of service attack due to an error within the Data Conversion logic. IBM X-Force ID: 177081.
